$interpreted: Innkeeper's Representative: We truly, sincerely, genuinely apologize for the disturbance caused by yesterday's rockfall~
Innkeeper's Representative: It's totally unprecedented in all the years the Spring Waters has been in business... Of course, nothing so dangerous as that will ever happen again!
Innkeeper's Representative: We'll soon be restarting the competition, so please feel safe and secure about entering. Rich and wonderful rewards await you all~~
Sione: About last night... Please don't trouble yourself over these criminals on my behalf. If you're poisoned again, you won't stand a chance of winning that medicine you need.
Nolva: I know, I won't get too close to them...
Nolva: As soon as I catch sight of them... I'll give you the signal with this red flare.
Sione: Good. Then—
Sione: Let's put our plans into action.
Nolva: Okay...!
Yao: Don't try it!
Reigning Champion: —S-so strong, he's too strong...!! I come here and take up the challenge each and every year, and this is the first time I've come across such a worthy opponent!
Passionate Challenger: Ohh!? You must be the reigning champ from these last few years!?
Excited Challenger: He bested the Master with ease. Now none of these youngsters stand a chance~
Yao: Get outta here!!
Reigning Champion: I... I'm going home to train myself up, but I'll be back!!
Nolva: (...Huh? What's going on there? What's all the fuss about...)
Nolva: (Forget this... I should hurry up and find that suspect! Mister Yao said she was frail and...)
Frail Young Lady: Excuse me.
Nolva: Sorry! P-please...
Frail Young Lady: ......
Nolva: (What's the hurry... Is she chasing something? And her face...)
Nolva: (—has a purple scar!?)
Yao: (It's quiet... Too quiet.)
Yao: (I don't see any signs of mass fainting this time, except for those who knocked themselves out by brawling. But there's clearly a lot fewer people...)
Yao: (Have they given up on their dirty tricks for this contest? Or have they simply found a better way to administer the drug?)
Nolva: Mister Yao! Watch out!
Yao: ...You're finally here?
Nolva: (Did we... succeed?)
Yao: (Ha... They miscalculated the range of their attack... That blow wasn't enough to slay her—Damnit!)
Sione: I saw your signal! Did you clash with the suspect? Where is she?
Nolva: She... She was pushed into the water by Yao, maybe she drowned...
Sione: Did she flee...?
Sione: She can't have gotten far if she was injured... Nolva, can you lend us a hand?
Sione: Keep searching!
Little Bro: ...Big Bro, Big Sis! You said she's been harmed!?
Big Bro: I saw it clearly, she took a hard blow and fell into the water... Fortunately she wasn't caught. She blended in with the disqualified contestants and fled the scene...
Little Bro: Does this mean it's time for Plan B!?
Little Bro: B-but if we do that, there'll be countless casualties among the guests...
Innkeeper's Representative: Who cares about some strangers' lives? What are they, compared to your own flesh and blood!?
Innkeeper's Representative: If Sis is injured, she doesn't stand a chance of snatching the crown—We have to do like we discussed and thoroughly destroy the competition...!!
Innkeeper's Representative: (Here we go...)
Innkeeper's Representative: What's the matter? Something need fixing? Big Bro! Go down and take a look...
Izumi: Didn't you just say you had a urgent bathroom emergency~ What're you doing out here?
Innkeeper's Representative: Izumi, y-you're...
Innkeeper's Representative: ...No wonder there was nothing happening after the sluice gates were opened, it was you—you already activated the backup gates downstream...
Izumi: Yep, good thing I sent someone to keep an eye on you lot, else there'd be an almighty mess of corpses to clean up down there~
Innkeeper's Representative: Why didn't you expose me earlier, if you already knew everything!!
Izumi: Why? I'm not in any hurry~ It's a good show you're putting on, so why not let it go on a little longer?
Izumi: But it's a real shame...
Izumi: Your character gets her comeuppance here~
Izumi: Hah? Oh, blast it~
Izumi: I forgot the reserve sluice hasn't been properly maintained in years...
